<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 px-4">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>

  <div class="prose prose-pink max-w-none text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-4">
    <p>
      <strong>ParroByte CRM</strong> ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
      This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our CRM platform.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and password (encrypted).</li>
      <li><strong>WhatsApp Data:</strong> Messages, contacts, and session information you choose to sync.</li>
      <li><strong>Social Media Data:</strong> Instagram and Facebook page details, comments, and access tokens (stored securely).</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with our platform to improve services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
      <li>To provide and maintain our CRM services.</li>
      <li>To automate WhatsApp, Instagram, and Facebook responses based on your configured rules.</li>
      <li>To send billing notifications and service updates.</li>
      <li>To improve platform performance and security.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <p>
      All data is stored on secure servers with encryption. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.
      Access tokens for social media platforms are encrypted at rest and only used for automation you explicitly configure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We integrate with WhatsApp Web, Facebook Graph API, Instagram Graph API, and Razorpay for payments.
      These services have their own privacy policies. We only request the minimum permissions needed for functionality.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      You can delete your account and all associated data at any time by contacting support.
      You can also disconnect WhatsApp sessions and social media accounts from your dashboard.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us through the Help Center in your dashboard.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
